<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Pocket Store</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; width: 100%; height: 100%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #f54e84, #b755ee); display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;">

    <div style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; padding: 0;">

        <div style="font-size: 35px; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff; position: absolute; top: 10px; left: 10px;">
            Pocket Store
        </div>

        <!-- Welcome email box -->
        <div style="background-color: white; border-top-left-radius: 150px; border-top-right-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 150px; border-bottom-left-radius: 150px; padding: 20px; text-align: center; width: calc(100% - 44px); max-width: 600px;  box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); margin: 0 auto;"> 

            <!-- Header -->
            <h1 style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 20px; color: #333333; margin-bottom: 28px;">Welcome to Pocket Store!</h1>

            <!-- Intro text -->
            <p style="font-size: 15px; color: #333333; margin-bottom: 19px;">
                Thank you for verifying your email <strong>{{email}}</strong> with Pocket Store! We're excited to have you with us.
            </p>

            <!-- Next steps -->
            <p style="font-size: 15px; color: #333333; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                You can now explore our services and features, designed to help you get the most out of your experience.
            </p>

            <!-- Encouragement -->
            <p style="font-size: 15px; color: #333333; margin-top: 15px;">
                If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to our support team. We're here to help!
            </p>

            <!-- Closing note -->
            <p style="font-size: 10px; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                We look forward to supporting you on your journey <br>with Pocket Store!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
